description	"Aqualish Mercenary

^2Weaponry:
- Blaster Pistol (1)
- DVX-9 Disruptor Rifle (2)
- 2 EMP Grenades

^6Equipment:
- Electroinoculars
- Advanced Medpac (50HP+)

^8Attributes:
- Heal (1)

^3Abilities:
- Dodge (3) ^3[CS1]
- Gun Kick ^3[CS3]

The Aqualish were tusked bipeds from the planet Ando whose appearance combined aspects of arachnids and aquatic mammals. Aqualish had a reputation for being nasty, crude and aggressive, and generally pursued off-world careers as mercenaries, bounty hunters and pirates."